Diana PENG, as Administratrix of the Estate of Alfred T.C. Peng, Tzuli Hsu, Joseph Huang, Stephen Huang, Pen Fa Lee and Veronica Wan, as Administratrix of the Estate of Chee C. Wan, Plaintiffs-Respondents,
v.
LAW OFFICE OF FENG LI, Defendant,
and
Feng Li, Defendant-Petitioner. C-982 September Term 2016
079415 Supreme Court of New Jersey. July 20, 2017

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003280-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
